      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s spec, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and rod bearing service, ensuring the high-pressure internals are track-ready. While showing honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
